    • execute

      public void execute​(Game game, it.polimi.ingsw.IntelliCranio.network.Packet packet) throws it.polimi.ingsw.IntelliCranio.server.exceptions.InvalidArgumentsException
      Execute the action relative to the code received with packet. Actions for this state: SELECT_CARD: Choose a card giving row and column coordinates RES_FROM_DEPOT: Pick a resource from warehouse RES_FROM_STRONG: Pick a resource from strongbox RES_FROM_CARD: Pick a resource from a Leader DEPOT card CANCEL: Cancel all the changes and go back to initial config. CONFIRM: Lock the selection to prevent changes SELECT_SLOT: After confirm, select a dev card slot to put the card

      Parameters:
      game - The game to update
      packet - Packet received from client
